data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of the highly sought after neighborhood of Dolan Creek.  In the kitchen, you'll be greeted with a cozy, window reading nook where you can drink your morning coffee and enjoy the beautiful view! It also boasts a stylish island, for meal preparation and entertaining guests.  The finished basement boasts the potential for the addition of 2 extra bedrooms and is already plumbed in for a 3rd bathroom. The possibilities are endless for a home office, playroom or a comfortable retreat!  The backyard is spacious and covered in vibrant green grass.  As an added bonus, this home sits on .041 acres and has plenty of room to park your toys!  With the capability of being a stylish, 6 bedroom-3 bathroom home, this asking price is a steal and is sure to go fast!  Listed by Hayley and Ryan Klima with eXp Realty Text or call Hayley or Ryan today to schedule your showing today!  Hayley 605-641-8515 Ryan 605-490-0796
